text: PRESS RELEASE: Roberts: Hold Remains Absent White House Assurance Not to Send #GITMO Terrorists to Kansas https://t.co/l7BcxEWsXc
name: Pat Roberts

text: ICYMI here is my speech on the Fanning nom & WH refusal to assure me no terrorists from #GITMO will be sent to KS. https://t.co/LFpL5qXRfr
name: Pat Roberts

text: If the plans from the administration rule out Ft. Leavenworth as an option for the relocation of #GITMO, all they have to do is tell me.
name: Pat Roberts

text: But make no mistake, I remain adamantly opposed to placing #GITMO detainees anywhere on the U.S. mainland.
name: Pat Roberts

text: It is what Kansans expect and have demanded of me.
name: Pat Roberts

text: This hold is one of the tools afforded to me as a US Senator & I will do everything in my power to protect the national security of the U.S.
name: Pat Roberts

text: All I am asking is for the @WhiteHouse to assure me Ft. Leavenworth is NOT a viable alternative.
name: Pat Roberts

text: I have reviewed the latest assessment & it's apparent that it’s virtually impossible to safely relocate terrorists to Ft. Leavenworth
name: Pat Roberts

text: The admin. refused to come forward w/ a real plan to re-locate the prisoners, instead of a weak attempt to honor a campaign promise.
name: Pat Roberts

text: We should be angry at the @WhiteHouse that intends to ignore laws & wants to bring terrorists to our shores.
name: Pat Roberts

text: w/ the threat of executive order, I have little choice but to do what I can to block the transfer of #GITMO detainees to Ft. Leavenworth.
name: Pat Roberts

text: After much study & review, I can name you countless reasons why this plan is wrong. It is also illegal, which @POTUS' cabinet acknowledges.
name: Pat Roberts

text: He insists on transferring the remaining #GITMO detainees to a site on the US the mainland, w/ Ft. Leavenworth under serious consideration.
name: Pat Roberts

text: As I have publicly stated from the beginning, my issue is not w/ the nominee, but w/ POTUS who continues to insist on closing #GITMO this yr
name: Pat Roberts

text: It is my deep respect & concern for our men & women in uniform & all those at Ft. Leavenworth that has compelled me to hold @POTUS' nominee.
name: Pat Roberts

text: I support Fanning to be Secretary of the @USArmy. KS is the proud home to 2 Army posts &I want the Army to have a highly-qualified Secretary
